---
import Layout from '../../Layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Tyler Teuber | Frontend Developer — MultiTracks Application" description="Portfolio of Tyler Teuber, Frontend Developer applying to MultiTracks.com. Church tech experience, AI-first workflow, and deep audio domain knowledge.">

<!-- Fixed Navbar -->
<nav id="navbar">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="#hero" class="nav-logo">TT</a>
    <button id="menu-toggle" class="menu-toggle" aria-label="Toggle menu">
      <span class="bar"></span>
      <span class="bar"></span>
      <span class="bar"></span>
    </button>
    <ul id="nav-links" class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#what-i-bring" class="nav-link">What I Bring</a></li>
      <li><a href="#projects" class="nav-link">Projects</a></li>
      <li><a href="#experience" class="nav-link">Experience</a></li>
      <li><a href="#skills" class="nav-link">Skills</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact" class="nav-link">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- Hero -->
<section id="hero" class="hero">
  <div class="grid-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <p class="hero-label">Frontend Developer</p>
      <h1 class="hero-name">Tyler Teuber</h1>
      <p class="hero-tagline">Building tools that give worship teams<br>more time for what really matters.</p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="#what-i-bring" class="btn btn-primary">What I Bring</a>
        <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-secondary">View Projects</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-portrait">
      <div class="portrait-frame">
        <img src="/Images/Portrait.jpg" alt="Tyler Teuber" />
        <div class="portrait-glow"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="led-strip hero-led">
    <span class="led"></span><span class="led"></span><span class="led"></span>
    <span class="led"></span><span class="led"></span><span class="led"></span>
    <span class="led"></span><span class="led"></span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- What I Bring -->
<section id="what-i-bring" class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">What I Bring to MultiTracks</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle reveal">Specific strengths that map to what you're looking for.</p>
    <div class="callout-grid">

      <div class="callout-card reveal">
        <div class="callout-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a4 4 0 0 0-4 4c0 2 1 3.5 4 5.5C15 9.5 16 8 16 6a4 4 0 0 0-4-4z"/><path d="M8.5 14.5A7 7 0 0 0 5 21h14a7 7 0 0 0-3.5-6.5"/><circle cx="12" cy="17" r="1"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="callout-title">Agentic Coding & AI-First</h3>
        <p class="callout-text">I actively use Claude Code for AI-assisted development. This isn't aspirational — it's my daily workflow. This portfolio was built with it.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="callout-card reveal">
        <div class="callout-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z"/><path d="M12 6v4"/><path d="M9 14h6"/><path d="M9 18h6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="callout-title">Church Tech Experience</h3>
        <p class="callout-text">When my church plant wasn't using MultiTracks, I advocated for it and personally implemented Playback, ChartBuilder, and RehearsalMix — integrating them with Planning Center and ProPresenter. Over a year in, the team loves it. I also built a Sermon Slide Generator used weekly at The Redemption Church.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="callout-card reveal">
        <div class="callout-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/><line x1="14" y1="4" x2="10" y2="20"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="callout-title">Frontend Expertise</h3>
        <p class="callout-text">HTML, CSS, JavaScript, TypeScript, React, Next.js — the core of what you need. I write clean, maintainable UI code every day.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="callout-card reveal">
        <div class="callout-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="callout-title">Team Player</h3>
        <p class="callout-text">Led a team of 5 interns at Kill That Noise. Teach and mentor students at Coding Mind. I thrive in collaborative environments.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="callout-card reveal">
        <div class="callout-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 18V5l12-2v13"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="16" r="3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="callout-title">Audio + Code</h3>
        <p class="callout-text">I play electric guitar on the worship team and volunteer on the audio team every week. My Audio Technology background combined with real production experience means I understand your domain from the stage and the booth.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="callout-card reveal">
        <div class="callout-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="callout-title">Self-Motivated Learner</h3>
        <p class="callout-text">Self-taught with guidance from a Senior Software Architect mentor since 2022. I take initiative and ship.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Projects -->
<section id="projects" class="section section-alt">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Projects</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle reveal">Selected work — ordered by relevance to MultiTracks.</p>
    <div class="projects-list">

      <!-- Sermon Slide Generator -->
      <div class="project-card reveal">
        <div class="project-image">
          <img src="/Images/SermonSlides/SermonSlidesGenerator.png" alt="Sermon Slide Generator" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="project-badge">Already building for the church</div>
        </div>
        <div class="project-info">
          <h3 class="project-title">Sermon Slide Generator</h3>
          <p class="project-desc">Python automation tool for church staff at The Redemption Church. Web scrapes sermon outlines and generates presentation-ready PDFs — used in service every week.</p>
          <div class="project-tech">
            <span class="tech-tag">Python</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">HTML/CSS/JS</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Web Scraping</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Synthesizer VST -->
      <div class="project-card reveal">
        <div class="project-image">
          <img src="/Images/Synth/Synth.png" alt="Synthesizer VST Plugin" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="project-badge">Deep audio technology understanding</div>
        </div>
        <div class="project-info">
          <h3 class="project-title">Synthesizer VST Plugin</h3>
          <p class="project-desc">Subtractive synthesizer with gesture-based UI and a Juno-inspired sound engine. Built from scratch in C++ with JUCE — real-time DSP and custom graphics.</p>
          <div class="project-tech">
            <span class="tech-tag">C++</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">JUCE</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">DSP</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content Blocker -->
      <div class="project-card reveal">
        <div class="project-image">
          <img src="/Images/Blocker/WebsiteBlocker.png" alt="Content Blocker" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="project-info">
          <h3 class="project-title">Content Blocker</h3>
          <p class="project-desc">Website and application blocking tool for Arch Linux + Hyprland. Full-stack with a React/Tailwind frontend and Flask backend.</p>
          <div class="project-tech">
            <span class="tech-tag">Python</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">TypeScript</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">React</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Flask</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Experience -->
<section id="experience" class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Experience</h2>
    <div class="timeline">

      <div class="timeline-item reveal">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <span class="timeline-date">Aug 2024 — Present</span>
          <h3 class="timeline-title">Teacher / Assistant Manager</h3>
          <p class="timeline-company">Coding Mind &middot; Redmond, WA</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item reveal">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <span class="timeline-date">Jun — Oct 2023</span>
          <h3 class="timeline-title">Web Developer Intern</h3>
          <p class="timeline-company">Kill That Noise &middot; Remote</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item reveal">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <span class="timeline-date">Sep — Dec 2022</span>
          <h3 class="timeline-title">Data Engineering Intern</h3>
          <p class="timeline-company">DeveloperDB &middot; Remote</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Skills -->
<section id="skills" class="section section-alt">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Skills</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle reveal">Organized by relevance to the role.</p>
    <div class="skills-grid">

      <div class="skill-group reveal">
        <h3 class="skill-group-title">Core Frontend</h3>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">HTML</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">CSS</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Sass</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">JavaScript</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">TypeScript</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-group reveal">
        <h3 class="skill-group-title">Frameworks</h3>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">React</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Next.js</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Tailwind CSS</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Svelte</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-group reveal">
        <h3 class="skill-group-title">Backend</h3>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">Python</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Node.js</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Nest.js</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Flask</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Prisma</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-group reveal">
        <h3 class="skill-group-title">Tools</h3>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">Git</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Linux</span>
          <span class="skill-tag highlight">Claude Code (AI-First)</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Selenium</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Contact -->
<section id="contact" class="section">
  <div class="section-inner contact-inner">
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Let's Build Something Meaningful</h2>
    <p class="contact-text reveal">I'd love to help MultiTracks empower worship teams around the world. Let's talk.</p>
    <div class="contact-links reveal">
      <a href="https://github.com/TTeuber" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-link">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/></svg>
        GitHub
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/tyler-teuber/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-link">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
        LinkedIn
      </a>
      <a href="mailto:tyler@example.com" class="contact-link">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="M22 7l-10 6L2 7"/></svg>
        Email
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* =========================================
     BASE & RESET
     ========================================= */
  * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
    scroll-padding-top: 5rem;
  }

  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
    background: #111110;
    color: #d6d3d1;
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* =========================================
     GRID OVERLAY
     ========================================= */
  .grid-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  /* =========================================
     NAVBAR
     ========================================= */
  #navbar {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(17, 17, 16, 0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.15);
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }

  .nav-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0.9rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #d97706;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .nav-link {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #a8a29e;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    position: relative;
  }

  .nav-link:hover,
  .nav-link.active {
    color: #d97706;
  }

  .nav-link.active::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -4px;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: #d97706;
    border-radius: 1px;
  }

  .menu-toggle {
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 5px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 4px;
  }

  .menu-toggle .bar {
    width: 24px;
    height: 2px;
    background: #a8a29e;
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .menu-toggle.open .bar:nth-child(1) {
    transform: rotate(45deg) translate(5px, 5px);
  }

  .menu-toggle.open .bar:nth-child(2) {
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .menu-toggle.open .bar:nth-child(3) {
    transform: rotate(-45deg) translate(5px, -5px);
  }

  /* =========================================
     LED STRIP
     ========================================= */
  .led-strip {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .led {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #d97706;
    box-shadow: 0 0 6px #d97706, 0 0 12px rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.3);
    animation: led-pulse 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .led:nth-child(2n) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .led:nth-child(3n) { animation-delay: 0.7s; }
  .led:nth-child(5n) { animation-delay: 1.1s; }

  @keyframes led-pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.4; }
    50% { opacity: 1; }
  }

  .hero-led {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
  }

  /* =========================================
     HERO
     ========================================= */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 7rem 1.5rem 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(170deg, #1a1918 0%, #111110 60%, #0f0e0d 100%);
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 3rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .hero-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #d97706;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fafaf9;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
    color: #a8a29e;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  .hero-ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* Buttons */
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.25s;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: #d97706;
    color: #111110;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #f59e0b;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.35);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: #d97706;
    border: 1px solid rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.4);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: #d97706;
    background: rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.08);
  }

  /* Portrait */
  .hero-portrait {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .portrait-frame {
    position: relative;
    width: 280px;
    height: 280px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 3px solid rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.3);
  }

  .portrait-frame img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .portrait-glow {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -4px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    background: conic-gradient(from 0deg, transparent 0%, rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.4) 25%, transparent 50%, rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.2) 75%, transparent 100%) border-box;
    -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) padding-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
    -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
    mask-composite: exclude;
    animation: glow-spin 8s linear infinite;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  @keyframes glow-spin {
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }

  /* =========================================
     SECTIONS
     ========================================= */
  .section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .section-alt {
    background: #1a1918;
  }

  .section-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fafaf9;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #78716c;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  /* =========================================
     CALLOUT CARDS
     ========================================= */
  .callout-grid {
    display: grid;
